# Get an API key at https://resend.com — required for the Feedback button
# Never commit real keys; copy this file to .env.local and paste your key there.
RESEND_API_KEY=

# Optional: where feedback emails are delivered (defaults to site.email in src/lib/site.ts)
# FEEDBACK_TO_EMAIL=

# Optional: From address. Until you verify a domain in Resend, use:
#   Portfolio feedback <onboarding@resend.dev>
# After domain verification, e.g. Feedback <feedback@yourdomain.com>
# FEEDBACK_FROM=
